{"tid":492585,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"部分公屋仔真係煩撚到仆街","createTime":"2017-12-07T16:19:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-18T03:29:52.000Z","uid":143768,"like":11,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d29f53a1f6d68743ac3933788bcd6ba520d8993c","tid":492585,"uid":143768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T16:19:26.000Z","msg":"點睇住公屋但成身潮野既人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/492417/page/3?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/492417/page/3?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n睇完呢個post就覺得有啲公屋仔真係井底之蛙<br />\n基本上每次有關公屋嘅post就會有呢班人出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n通常唔理三七廿一，第一句就會講租金 ：<br />\n公屋交完份租，份糧都好似冇郁過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  班私樓傻仔死供爛供 份糧都冇咗大半<br />\n又唔諗下根本唔少人都一早供完 另外嗰啲人又好撚短視，講到無憂無慮去下旅行幾撚開心咁。係呀，你地咪永遠停留係一年去兩次日本呢個階段囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n有時講完租金又會扯去講屋企有咩壞，房屋署嗰啲會負責搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n痴撚線，呢啲野都好拎嚟打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  屌你老味間屋唔係你㗎嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  政府梗係負責啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<br />\n公屋又要扣分，對面住個痴線佬日日投訴你，分分鐘都食你幾分。當你俾人扣剩幾分，都唔知你生活點過，行步路都唔敢太大力 <br />\n<br />\n當然我信有大部分住公屋既都唔會咁，所以我一直都講係部分人。大佬，住公屋本身就冇乜問題，你安份守己咪算囉，你住公屋既都知你入息唔會太高，你又何必充大頭鬼呢？？ 正常人地都唔會主動出聲串你啦。但係嗰班人次次就好似冇讀過書咁，一講就講到公屋冇住過就走寶咁，人地先開聲講你公屋問題咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5798418b8ade02d0e3fe3b8f6e8e0f0dc2ed7fe0","tid":492585,"uid":24472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T17:19:41.000Z","msg":"你咪比佢地攞黎打j囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c184c3739f108198d8a4f8ba3a97e760e2cb7b5","tid":492585,"uid":73109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T02:08:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0fc497fa630d968e9c60446dfad41f87d0e7d571","tid":492585,"uid":985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T02:10:57.000Z","msg":"其實有好多人仲以為住公屋就唔超入息，其實大部分都超，除非岩岩上樓。<br />\n不過入息唔高加無料係事實。"},{"pid":"19fe5e0c50762def102a7fa8de37ba84339e38c7","tid":492585,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T02:59:18.000Z","msg":"買左呢？"},{"pid":"a2a409c3523203009ae65d8192e6d4a5d6de852b","tid":492585,"uid":73109,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:56:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e387b008f19b6a2d82858343a0177a928382ce3f","tid":492585,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T08:11:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4200eddf9e7de9a8c92ec416388b6e3d1a777d81","tid":492585,"uid":156422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T03:29:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}